data.title: Rasheed Wallace Introduced As Newest Celtic
data.meta_description: Marc D'Amico July 9, 2009 Celtics.com Five familiar faces of the Celtics' basketball family took the stage today to introduce their newest member, four-time All-Star forward/center Rasheed Wallace. With President of Basketball Operations Danny Ainge, Head Coach Doc Rivers and his new running mates, Ray Allen, Paul Pierce and Kevin Garnett by his side, Wallace met the Boston press for the first time.
